// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1792 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 574ab78d-1ea7-5aa1-b8c0-22f755978b1c

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
